	   <tr><td colspan=2>Talendor in Skyfire Mountains can drop the torn, burnt book.  Gorenaire in the Dreadlands can drop the torn, frost covered book.  Faydedar in Timorous Deep (not the triggered lv 55 one for druid epic), and Severilous in the Emerald Jungle have a rare chance of dropping either book.  The Kunark dragons are quite a bit harder than their old world counterparts so be careful.  I hope this info was helpful.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ryudaian Foehammer<br>By Far The Worst Paladin In EverQuest</td></tr>
